Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.29,0:01:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, I know this makes it the fifth time today, \Nbut in honor of our man Shimano tying the knot...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.18,0:01:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.59,0:01:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys, that's enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.21,0:01:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.11,0:01:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you have to pick Shimano of all people...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:28.87,0:01:31.61,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Shima-chan sure did something hurtful. {shima = affectionate shortening of shimano}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of people crying here today.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.83,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear your wife's a real beauty.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.72,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I wouldn't go {\i1}that{\i0} far.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.37,0:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They just used to say she was the prettiest girl at my university.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, lucky you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.86,0:01:46.37,Overlap,,0,0,0,,You weasel!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.00,0:01:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.51,0:01:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This, plus that informal job offer, \Nand now it's smooth sailing for you, huh? {就職も内定したし}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.89,0:01:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceremony's tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.89,0:01:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in Osaka. \NThat's where her parents live.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hopping on a plane first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.02,0:02:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why you're cutting loose tonight, huh? {because it's his bachelor party}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.96,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Well, no, actually... {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.14,0:02:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, this guy was \Nsuch a straight arrow back in college!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.00,0:02:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So we figured, as his buddies, \Nwe ought to give him a proper send-off tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable. \NWhat, you gonna take him to a brothel later? {soapland - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Types_of_prostitution_in_modern_Japan#Soapland}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with that out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Party's over for you at eight tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.51,0:02:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.57,0:02:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what happened to that big send-off \Nyou guys were setting up?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.00,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,9 p.m., Tokyo to Osaka, Hikari Line. \NPrivate compartment, first class. {lit: Green Car - the highest class car on shinkansen}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.16,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the Cinderella Express \Nthat's been the talk of the town. {/so-called}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.47,0:02:52.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.09,0:02:57.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,Clever name, that "Cinderella Express." A farewell stage for businessmen who have to work away from home. {lit: place of goodbye for those away from home,  moving to a different location to start a new job}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,Guess that'll be me \Nonce I start working full-time.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.67,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, what kind of "send-off" is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.94,0:03:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they just trying to show me \Nmy bleak salaryman future?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! {kidna meaningless, maybe hello there}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.99,0:03:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you... {doing here}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say you pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Chima.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.69,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's my first day on the job, \Nso take care of me. {she just says "job" here but in manga she says explicitly "my first day prostituting myself"}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.52,0:03:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,On the job?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Work.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.41,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're 17?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! And it's my very first day here! {on the job}{to avoid repetition}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll give you lots of service!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.22,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hold on a second! \NI was already paid in advance to entertain you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.42,0:05:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{nothing meaningful}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, pushy. {/you're a violent type}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.48,0:06:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,D-D-Don't just say stuff like that so loud!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.80,0:06:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You said this is your first day on the job...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.09,0:06:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. So no need to worry about diseases. You're safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.55,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Those idiots...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all ages, they picked a 17 year old... {his classmates? who were at the bachelor party}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.53,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! If you don't believe me, \NI can show you a medical certificate.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.41,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Look, that's not it. \NWhy start something like this at your age? For money?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.85,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! What's with that gloomy thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.10,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I wanna have sex, obviously!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.08,0:06:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is with this weird cheerfulness?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So, shall we?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.66,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sh-Shall we," she says...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.11,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends already paid me, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.49,0:07:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll give you lots of service.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.94,0:07:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.18,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're taking the last train to Osaka, \Nhow are you getting back?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.49,0:07:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my home's in Osaka. \NI just came up here and I'm heading right back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,First day on the job and already optimizing it, huh? Not bad at all. {lit: already making money - not sure how that makes sense, maybe he means "cutting corners/doing things to save more money"}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad with that Kansai dialect! {guess that's why the prev line sounded weird}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll go Kansai style on this too. {lit: do it in osaka dialect}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you mean, "on this too"?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.73,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.67,0:07:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, time is money! {lit: we're running out of time - kansai ben has a lot of paraphrases for making money so from here on I'll be trying to accentuate that}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better enjoy yourself properly, big brother!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.13,0:07:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's only 17! \NCan I really?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.67,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I'm getting married tomorrow anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's ever a time to do this, it's now.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.25,0:08:27.12,Song,,0,0,0,,This feeling's up to you, thirsty as you want {song is あなたまかせのキャンティ, absolutely no trace of lyrics, I think both songs in this were written for the OVA and never released outside of it, going by ear}{??? maybe "tasty" or "Thursday"}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.12,0:08:30.84,Song,,0,0,0,,Feeling your fingertips,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.84,0:08:34.59,Song,,0,0,0,,making me hot like brandy {??? brandy?}{熱い行動のブランデー, idk much what to do with this one either}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.59,0:08:37.63,Song,,0,0,0,,{meaningless, sabatotudatuda?}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.81,0:08:41.15,Song,,0,0,0,,Baby
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.64,0:08:45.13,Song,,0,0,0,,No rushing it, Baby
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.13,0:08:51.68,Song,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Darling?\NBest wishes for you {目出度いでよ}{???}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.14,0:08:57.48,Song,,0,0,0,,I get it in a flash—telepathy
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.99,0:09:01.28,Song,,0,0,0,,One wink and it's OK
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.28,0:09:08.42,Song,,0,0,0,,Neon lights sparkling\NLike a paradise in space
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.42,0:09:10.83,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.83,0:09:17.43,Song,,0,0,0,,Baby, snap your fingers
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.43,0:09:21.20,Song,,0,0,0,,Baby, we can go anywhere
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.77,Song,,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.27,0:09:25.73,Song,,0,0,0,,to a world of dreams
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.87,0:09:46.29,Song,,0,0,0,,Relax, roll it {loli?}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.29,0:09:49.55,Song,,0,0,0,,Time it, falling {??? falling?}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.55,0:09:53.22,Song,,0,0,0,,Even if the times change,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.66,0:09:57.25,Song,,0,0,0,,man and woman—candy
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.25,0:10:00.05,Song,,0,0,0,,{meaningless, sabatotudatuda?}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.44,0:10:06.19,Song,,0,0,0,,Baby, stop playing games
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.19,0:10:09.76,Song,,0,0,0,,Baby, be honest
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.76,0:10:14.31,Song,,0,0,0,,Darling, it's so frustrating {???}{焦れったい}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.10,0:10:38.72,Song,,0,0,0,,Dua dua darling\NDua dua darling
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.54,0:11:25.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,D-Did she say it's her first day today...? {? the line is "たしかに年期が入ってる" from manga but not sure what it has to do with "apprenticeship; indentureship"; that stroke on the glass is the tally for how many times they've come, and that's something only experienced women do ig?}{doing a tally implies she's expecting to do it many more times (else she wouldn't be counting), so that implies she's experienced enough to not just figuratively die after one time; also changed the line because you kinda missed the point of the protagonist asking himself if that's really her first day/if she's still learning the ropes}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Another round?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Not so fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.58,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, when was your first time?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Scissors?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Second year of middle school. {sounds like "12" but i know it's chuu ni from manga... or is it? second year of middle school is like 13-14 anyway}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a high schooler.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.20,0:11:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd do all my summer homework for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What, really?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it was my first time, \Nit didn't hurt all that much.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I've probably done it with dozens of guys.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.35,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They buy me clothes or give me spending money. {pocket money/allowance}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.19,0:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, what that basically means is...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.35,0:12:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I thought, if I'm going to do it, \NI might as well make it my job.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So today's my first day on the job.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You got lucky, big brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{shocked}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.85,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, wait... Does that mean it's been your job \Nsince your very first time?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.79,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong! I didn't get paid that time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.27,0:12:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting paid in money \Nor in summer homework are the same thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.86,0:12:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting compensation for sex \Nis the most primitive kind of job there is. {SEXに代償を\Nもらうってのは\Nいっとー原始的な\N売春なの!!!!}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.72,0:12:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't that what they call free love?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.74,0:12:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.30,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk... Really? \NI wonder how much more I could have made by now. {in manga: How many millions of yen have I lost so far?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.61,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being careful, right? \NAbout pregnancy and diseases?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.00,0:12:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been using an IUD \Nsince my third year of middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,An IUD? What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't know?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}should{\i0} I know?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{to begin with, }And you, as a high school student...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.61,0:12:57.69,Overlap,,0,0,0,,It's called an intrauterine device. {子宮内避妊具リング = intrauterine contraception ring - aka ota's ring - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tenrei_%C5%8Cta}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.69,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.45,0:13:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you get regular checkups, it's the safest.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.25,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Safe, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.51,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I get to feel good and, on top of that, \Nthe guy gives me something in return.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.66,0:13:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So you consider {\i1}that{\i0} your calling, huh? {/vocation}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.88,0:13:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe not that serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,let's go one more time!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.93,0:15:18.30,Top,,0,0,0,,Shin Osaka! Shin Osaka! {station}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap! Oh crap! Oh crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.17,0:15:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I've gotta hurry back or Mom'll kill me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.49,0:15:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If fate allows, let's meet again.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.10,0:15:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess there are girls like that too...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.22,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! The bride's changing, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.19,0:16:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are your manners, Chima? \NAt least greet your brother-in-law properly.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.65,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-My... Y-You're... my little sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.02,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that to yourself! \NYou really want to wreck your own wedding?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.62,0:16:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who'd be in trouble \Nif big sis found out.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here, you two?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's... I... S-So {\i1}she's{\i0} your little sister?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.06,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.49,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.31,0:17:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, she's been at an all-girls school \Nsince middle school, so she's not used to men. {men'eki = immunity/being accustomed (to)}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.09,0:17:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I wish she could interact with men \Nmore naturally, like a normal girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.14,0:17:22.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,N-Not used to men?! {men'eki}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.71,0:17:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So... if you try anything funny with her, \NI won't forgive you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you, dear groom.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.04,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is my bride!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.29,0:18:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right, she's also Chima's older sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.32,0:18:31.61,Top,,0,0,0,,Do you both vow, with lifelong resolve, \Nuntil death do you part?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.03,0:18:35.35,Top,,0,0,0,,In good times and in bad...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.55,0:18:40.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,God... how much do I really know \Nabout this woman, Emori Misa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know she had a little sister.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.79,0:18:49.30,Thought,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \Nwe've only known each other two years.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.30,0:18:52.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,Back in high school, \Nwas Misa maybe like Chima too?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.46,0:18:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimano Yuji.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimano Yuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you spacing out for?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.11,0:19:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ah... yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.89,0:19:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you take Emori Misa as your wife, \Nand vow to love and cherish her for life?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.52,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes, I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.62,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Emori Misa, do you take Shimano Yuji \Nas your husband, and vow to love him for life?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.63,0:19:31.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's right... there's no guarantee \NMisa wasn't like Chima once.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.19,0:19:33.44,Thought,,0,0,0,,No, no, wait a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.44,0:19:38.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,Last winter, when Misa and I first slept together, \Nshe was definitely a virgin.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.98,0:19:43.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,But wait, they say that kind of thing can be faked.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.70,0:19:48.00,Thought,,0,0,0,,After all, she's the sister of a girl \Nwho's been using birth control since middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.49,Thought,,0,0,0,,The rings?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.41,0:19:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{meaningless? just "gyan" in manga}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.02,0:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.63,0:20:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry! I'll get them!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.34,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, found it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, big brother!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.02,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you panicking? \NCalm down and finish the ceremony.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.66,0:20:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Yuji? \NKeep it together!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.31,0:20:27.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,This marriage feels doomed from the start... {like a mistake/slip up}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.29,0:21:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is your new place, huh?\NA brand-new condo!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.54,0:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.34,0:21:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.57,0:21:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure big brother's salary can cover it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.55,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji's father prepaid a full year of rent \Nas congratulations on his employment.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.06,0:21:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, darling?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.23,0:21:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.78,0:21:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.42,0:21:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima-chan, kids don't need \Nto worry about that stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.40,0:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids, you hear?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.34,0:21:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, as long as your parents let you sponge off them, \Nyou might as well milk it for all it's worth. {something in kansai, not sure but i think the meaning is this}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.48,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima, you may not like men, \Nbut try to get along, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.32,0:21:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji-san is your big brother now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.65,0:21:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you two take care of the luggage. \NI'll go greet our landlord.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.51,0:22:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you up to?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.99,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you tag along all the way to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, it's spring break.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.49,0:22:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! You've got some other scheme, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.45,0:22:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Tokyo has more customers or something!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.25,0:22:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.41,0:22:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You little...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.39,0:22:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Big bro...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.53,0:22:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.24,0:22:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,hate me that much?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.66,0:22:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, i-it's not like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.43,0:22:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God... I thought...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.10,0:22:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to have such a wonderful big brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.26,0:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hated me, I wouldn't know what to do...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.12,0:22:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'd do...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.02,0:22:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.17,0:22:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.87,0:22:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.41,0:23:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a soft touch, big bro!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.50,0:23:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you'll get played over and over. {??? something in kansai}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.16,0:23:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.26,0:23:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Chima-chan \Nreally does say the funniest things...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.55,0:23:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Chima-chan? Even among men, \Nthere are some who aren't scary at all, like my darling.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.18,0:23:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our landlord.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He lives on the second floor.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.75,0:23:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.27,0:23:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always reassuring having the landlord \Nliving nearby for management matters.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.16,0:23:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, likewise, pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.96,0:23:46.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,So that's the landlord, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:05.52,0:24:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.45,0:24:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.87,0:24:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! How long are you going to keep that up?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.06,0:24:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pity, isn't it? {??? can't hear shit and it's probably something in kansai}{可哀想ええんな}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.89,0:24:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you graduate, \Nfind yourself a good man soon too.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.22,0:24:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.54,0:24:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.84,0:24:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Watch the house and behave yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:40.06,0:24:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it? Don't you dare bring some guy into our bed!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.23,0:24:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:46.37,0:24:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Very!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.24,0:24:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.26,0:25:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This girl is... the new Shimano family's...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:51.18,0:25:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:53.34,0:25:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, lady!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.96,0:26:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm fine, really. \NI'm just a little anemic...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.83,0:26:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:07.48,0:26:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you don't look fine at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:10.55,0:26:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll walk you home.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:12.29,0:26:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:13.04,0:26:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... I can't go back \Nto my lonely room all by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:17.14,0:26:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, p-pull yourself together... please.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:23.78,0:26:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Guess I've no choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:31.86,0:26:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:40.86,0:26:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't worry. \NYou should rest a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.89,0:26:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife's out right now anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:44.94,0:26:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, take it easy. \NDon't move around too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:49.36,0:26:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:52.36,0:26:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:52.59,0:27:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I c-can't take it anymore! {/hold back/control myself}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:56.48,0:27:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing, mister?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:00.48,0:28:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, I won't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:04.63,0:28:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've waited so long for this, here I go! {???? not in manga and can't hear}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.93,0:28:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm scared! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:12.32,0:28:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:13.83,0:28:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Mister, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:17.98,0:28:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here now... {/let's see}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:19.77,0:28:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:21.00,0:28:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared! I... I'm still a virgin! {pure/chaste}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:29.07,0:28:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:30.91,0:28:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:32.75,0:28:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll enjoy it!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.93,0:28:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:36.97,0:28:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:38.37,0:28:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, it'd be rude to stop, wouldn't it? {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:41.54,0:28:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:43.02,0:28:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:43.80,0:28:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:45.32,0:28:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do anything bad to me, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:47.74,0:28:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you? Promise me!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:49.93,0:28:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I swear it! Absolutely!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:29.30,0:29:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:34.26,0:29:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! {I guess referring to that pale stain on the sheet since they couldn't show real blood for some reason?}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:35.55,0:29:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So when you said you were a virgin...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:40.01,0:29:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,i-it was true?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:42.26,0:29:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:46.03,0:29:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:47.92,0:29:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:50.42,0:29:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wouldn't do anything bad, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.76,0:29:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:54.69,0:29:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be separated \Nfrom my beloved sister. I want to live here.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:59.41,0:30:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? That's all?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:02.75,0:30:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got just the flat for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:04.12,0:30:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A 2DK for 110,000 a month. \NDeposit and key money... {2DK - basically 2DK apartment has two (often small) separate rooms, plus one combined dining space and kitchen. - https://redos.co.in/2dk-apartment-what-does-it-mean-and-is-it-right-for-you - maybe replace it with "two-room apartment" or something that's actually understandable by an american viewer?}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:07.63,0:30:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:09.42,0:30:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! First you do such a horrible thing \Nto a virgin high school girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:14.46,0:30:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a-and now you're trying to extort the deposit \Nand key money from me? That's terrible!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:19.59,0:30:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? N-No, I never intended to take \Nthat kind of money from you, young lady.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:27.06,0:30:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:27.94,0:30:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:29.15,0:30:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just the rent is fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:40.28,0:30:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably just planning to sneak over \Nto see me when your wife's not around.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:45.61,0:30:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.20,0:30:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults are disgusting!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:48.97,0:30:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm reporting you to the police \Nfor sexually assaulting a minor!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:57.99,0:31:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! O-Okay, okay!\N It's yours. For free! Free!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:09.38,0:31:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:58.43,0:31:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:01.04,0:32:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{??}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:03.50,0:32:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:32:05.29,0:32:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuji! Let go!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:13.12,0:32:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:15.32,0:32:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Newlyweds maybe?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:19.24,0:32:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't do that here in Waikiki. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:21.82,0:32:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They look silly. {/stupid}
Dialogue: 10,0:33:00.01,0:33:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:02.71,0:33:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.54,0:33:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In this long life ahead of us, \Nplease take care of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:17.10,0:33:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:17.93,0:33:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Likewise.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:33.54,0:33:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Yuji!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:24.88,0:34:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Yuji! It's our honeymoon.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:28.72,0:34:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... huh... {/yeah}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.84,0:34:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "uh-huh" me! \NIt's nothing to "uh-huh" about! {?? idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:33.51,0:34:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our honeymoon, \Nand your new wife is right in front of you...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:36.54,0:34:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what does this mean?! {/that's not an appropriate reaction/it's not this}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:51.67,0:34:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{?? kono?}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:03.59,0:35:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:35:14.68,0:35:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:16.46,0:35:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough! {/I don't care anymore}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:34.71,0:35:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those two now?
Dialogue: 10,0:35:36.42,0:35:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:35:43.78,0:35:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:14.67,0:36:18.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is only the beginning \Nof our misfortunes...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:25.64,0:36:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, that's everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:27.60,0:36:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:36.52,0:36:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, what lovely furniture!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:38.83,0:36:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's lucky! \NI want stuff like that too.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:42.20,0:36:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:43.70,0:36:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:47.82,0:36:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, take it up to the third floor! {she's saying that to the loaders}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:51.46,0:36:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chima!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:54.05,0:36:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo! Welcome back!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:58.92,0:37:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our place is on the fifth floor, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:01.74,0:37:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:03.07,0:37:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? You're living here now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:07.83,0:37:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, okay, okay... \NWhoops, sorry there!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.26,0:37:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave that over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:13.96,0:37:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:16.67,0:37:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my new place. {yoroshiku ne - kinda universal stock phrase, idk what it means here, maybe kinda like "we're neighbors now so let's get along"}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:17.97,0:37:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your place?! \NYou're still in high...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:20.67,0:37:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, yes. Whoa! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:23.70,0:37:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima-chan, where should this go?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:26.98,0:37:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There! The kitchen's in the back.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:29.99,0:37:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:31.30,0:37:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:34.42,0:37:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima! You're still in high school!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:37.39,0:37:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What about your school?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:39.60,0:37:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoka School for Girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:41.71,0:37:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, my school in Osaka \Nhas a sister school here. {not sure how that's supposed to work, in manga at least she explains she came here as an exchange student}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:45.46,0:37:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Hey now... Misa!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:48.53,0:37:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it fine?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:50.18,0:37:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once this girl makes up her mind, \Nshe won't budge.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:52.94,0:37:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Misa!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:56.48,0:37:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima! Just what are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:59.51,0:38:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:00.65,0:38:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "what" me! \NWh-Where did all this money come from!?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:04.57,0:38:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All these appliances and furniture—\Nwhere did you get the cash!?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:09.30,0:38:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Savings!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:10.66,0:38:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd believe that!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:13.01,0:38:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! I've loved saving money since I was three! {/made it my habit}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:17.68,0:38:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:18.96,0:38:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:36.16,0:38:39.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Chima sleeps with all these guys too...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:41.50,0:38:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Electronics! Electronics! \NElectronics! Electronics!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:44.97,0:38:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Electronics! Electronics! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:38:46.66,0:38:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dishes! Dishes! Dishes!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:52.15,0:38:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Silver spoons! Silver spoons! Silver spoons!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.16,0:39:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Piano! Piano! Piano!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:10.95,0:39:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Persian carpets!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:13.59,0:39:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{Waow!}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:16.68,0:39:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fully automatic washer with drying function!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:22.54,0:39:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Every woman's dream—a kitchen set \Nwith a dishwasher, electric hood, and dish dryer! {seems to be the japanese wasei-eigo for "kitchen set"}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:32.30,0:39:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,French Rococo canopy bed, \Nwith an ultra-hardened frame!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:36.86,0:39:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A sofa set! {????? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:37.48,0:39:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Car!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:38.14,0:39:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,45-inch color TV!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.66,0:39:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,An AC! {??? some **cooler I think?}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.86,0:39:42.59,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Whales, elephants, dolphins, seals, even hippos!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:47.45,0:39:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:48.28,0:39:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again, Yuji-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:51.96,0:39:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:03.23,0:40:06.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Yes, right... That's got to be it!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:06.65,0:40:11.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,Knowing her, who knows \Nwhat she'll pull next. All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:17.27,0:40:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come in. It's open!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:20.90,0:40:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chima, I've got something \Nto say to you, so listen carefully.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:25.12,0:40:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, as your big brother, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:34.42,0:40:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:38.45,0:40:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh brother, you can barely see Gemini tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:42.06,0:40:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ch-Chima-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:47.80,0:40:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect that. \NYou like stargazing?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:50.47,0:40:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:51.08,0:40:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? N-No, I mean, \NI didn't peg you for a romantic.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:56.20,0:40:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:57.21,0:41:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Gemini is made up of two stars, \NAlpha Castor and Beta Pollux.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:03.48,0:41:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pollux is the son of Zeus, the god of fire. \NCastor is the son of the King of Sparta. {??? some things are changed, like zeus became gausu somehow - is this intentional? is she supposed to be underinformed? castor was also kamatoru in prev line... were they going for some kind of legally distinct names or what?}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:12.17,0:41:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But they share the same mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:14.68,0:41:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:16.12,0:41:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Pollux, the god's child, was born because Leda, \Nthe Spartan queen, had an affair with Zeus.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:24.22,0:41:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A-An affair?!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:25.80,0:41:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Leda's own choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:28.44,0:41:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's still a wrong thing to do! {??? idk what's ikenai, cheating on your husband? why does it matter at all?}
Dialogue: 10,0:41:30.46,0:41:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's fine if you live here, \Nbut from now on...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:49.67,0:41:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no! \NWe can't do that sort of thing anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:53.71,0:41:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you and I are family now! {siblings}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:03.92,0:42:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. That's why, at the very least,
Dialogue: 10,0:42:10.24,0:42:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,just being near you, big bro...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:14.73,0:42:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:17.79,0:42:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling myself that
Dialogue: 10,0:42:20.32,0:42:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and continue with my life, quietly...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:25.83,0:42:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,living like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:28.88,0:42:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,all on my own. {/alone}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:30.11,0:42:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:31.17,0:42:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,does that mean you... {love me}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:34.65,0:42:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:36.30,0:42:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was love at first sight, my first one.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:41.58,0:42:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what it is? I had no idea...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:43.63,0:42:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And all this time I...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:48.68,0:42:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I even imagining?! {???}{referring to him imagining Chima fucking all those people a few minutes ago}
Dialogue: 10,0:42:53.55,0:42:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:55.16,0:42:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Forgive me.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:57.78,0:42:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Big bro!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:58.98,0:43:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Chima!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:09.50,0:43:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! {/no way!}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:11.21,0:43:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:12.34,0:43:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I'm talking about! {what you can't do/is wrong}
Dialogue: 10,0:43:16.79,0:43:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're cute when you're mad, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:25.04,0:43:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't win against you.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:27.41,0:43:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got no clue what's going \Nto happen from here on out...
Dialogue: 10,0:43:34.74,0:43:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Big bro,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:36.83,0:43:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 10,0:44:08.96,0:44:15.97,Song,,0,0,0,,{シンデレラは愛せない - I found this: https://utaten.com/lyric/to16064329/ - but it's garbage and the lyrics are blatantly wrong, safe to assume there was never a CD release either so going by ear, but it's not great} The train of love has calmed down and started moving
Dialogue: 10,0:44:15.97,0:44:21.23,Song,,0,0,0,,not knowing where it's headed, LOVE ME TONIGHT
Dialogue: 10,0:44:23.80,0:44:35.62,Song,,0,0,0,,A sigh echoes your name on a foggy windowpane\NA whisper in my ear—KISS ME TONIGHT
Dialogue: 10,0:44:38.43,0:44:55.06,Song,,0,0,0,,The temptation of your lips \Nscares me a little, deep in my heart
Dialogue: 10,0:44:55.06,0:45:02.62,Song,,0,0,0,,TRAIN TRAIN, if it's just my heart, I'll close my eyes
Dialogue: 10,0:45:02.62,0:45:09.87,Song,,0,0,0,,Take me deeper into dreams, I want to feel more
Dialogue: 10,0:45:09.87,0:45:17.15,Song,,0,0,0,,TRAIN TRAIN, I love you more than anyone\NBut why am I trembling?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:17.15,0:45:25.64,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm Cinderella, but I still can't love {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:41.52,0:45:48.88,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm going through the hesitation station of your railway
Dialogue: 10,0:45:48.88,0:45:53.55,Song,,0,0,0,,I hate being alone—STAR TONIGHT {????}{一人は嫌いよ}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:56.37,0:46:03.69,Song,,0,0,0,,I often get lost, but if it's with you, I want to get hurt
Dialogue: 10,0:46:03.69,0:46:08.22,Song,,0,0,0,,His kiss makes me skip a beat {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:10.92,0:46:27.54,Song,,0,0,0,,With a silent placid smile, what are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:27.54,0:46:35.21,Song,,0,0,0,,TRAIN TRAIN, if we're alone, take me with you{ねえ連れてって}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:35.21,0:46:42.48,Song,,0,0,0,,Because it aches, I want to be closer
Dialogue: 10,0:46:42.48,0:46:49.82,Song,,0,0,0,,TRAIN TRAIN, the midnight bell is ringing now {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:49.82,0:46:58.42,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm Cinderella, but I still can't love
Dialogue: 10,0:47:13.80,0:47:21.57,Song,,0,0,0,,TRAIN TRAIN, if it's just my heart, take me with you {ねえ連れてって}
Dialogue: 10,0:47:21.57,0:47:28.73,Song,,0,0,0,,Take me deeper into dreams, I want to feel more
Dialogue: 10,0:47:28.73,0:47:35.97,Song,,0,0,0,,TRAIN TRAIN, I love you more than anyone\NBut why am I trembling?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:35.97,0:47:45.28,Song,,0,0,0,,I'm Cinderella, but I still can't love
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.28,0:47:48.28,Song,,0,0,0,,
